values: Well I moved to New Mexico a few days ago. We stopped at Jimmy's on the way out in Tuscon. He's pretty awesome and nice especially. He's got a badass lifted van. Sounds really mean too. He also has a Subaru WRX stage 4 turbo . The boostmonster. Thats the first car I've ever felt boost in. It was cool. New Mexico is ok i guess weather is nice and all but i dont have many friends yet and even if i did they wouldnt replace the old ones. And I have been thinking alot about them too. One more than others. I'll update alot more than usual because I'm on broadband.

Yah I'm pissed beyond beleif.
